friday-2023-tech-deals-under-50-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23972578/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-50-cyber-monday</id><author><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T09:25:35-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T09:25:35-05:00</updated><title> Apple 设备上的“网络星期一”最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黄色的第 10 代 iPad，面朝上放在木桌上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jC11n2zd4486vWLn2Ew2O4aMBQs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72895666/226361_Apple_iPad_10.9_10th _gen_DSeifert_0001.6.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;第 10 代 iPad 在本网络星期一降至有史以来最低价格。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hjr3cC&quot;>;与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/2/2/23583501/apple-iphone -ipad-active-2-billion-devices-q1-2023&quot;>;超过 20 亿人&lt;/a>;使用其产品，可以肯定地说，苹果的产品是世界上最受欢迎的产品之一。因此，毫不奇怪，它们也是很棒的节日礼物——只要您能超越它们通常带来的高昂价格标签。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang &quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;MK5Pnu&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;网络星期一最佳优惠&quot;, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23973013/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;网络星期一 100 美元以下最佳优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;f5fVhl&quot;>;如果您错过了黑色星期五优惠，幸运的是，网络星期一优惠就在这里，降低了最新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com 的价格/Apple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized/dp/B0CHWRXH8B/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; 