quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;idm7Ct&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;bZLjoB&quot;>;例如，您仍然可以在购买许多受欢迎的礼物时获得大幅折扣，包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort -Wireless-Cancelling-Headphones/dp/B0CCZ1L489?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳机&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. amazon.com/Introducing-sound-compact-speaker-Lavender/dp/B09ZXJDSL5/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Amazon 的 Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 到 &lt;a href =“https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/roam”rel =“赞助nofollow noopener”目标=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Sonos Roam&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Kindle-Paperwhite-adjustable-Ad-Supported/dp/B08KTZ8249/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel= “赞助的 nofollow noopener” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Kindle Paperwhite&lt;/a>;。还有许多其他类型的小工具的优惠，包括手机、智能手表、耳机、充电器、玩具和各种配件。并非所有的优惠都是黑色星期五的剩菜。其他小工具现在甚至更便宜，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation/dp/B07K1WWBJK?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener &quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;第二代 Apple Pencil&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09M8LG59J?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;provided nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Yeedi Vac 2 Pro&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F% 2Fnanoleaf.me%2Fen-US%2Fproducts%2Fnanoleaf-shapes%2F%3Fcategory%3Dultra-black-triangles%26pack%3Dsmarter-kit%26size%3D9&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww。 theverge.com%2F23973013%2Fcyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Nanoleaf 形状超黑...&lt;/a>;&lt;/ p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23973013/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23973013/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23973013/cyber-monday-2023-best-early-deals-tech-headphones-gifts</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>这家公司刚刚给苹果MacBook Air装上了空气</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;两台薄笔记本电脑放在桌子上，屏幕上有基准。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/D7zHn41ClWae-G6dbKZY5q8GNtc=/0x336:4032x3024/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72905441/IMG_0906.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;加利福尼亚州圣何塞 Frore Systems 总部的两台 15 英寸 M2 MacBook Air 笔记本电脑。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Sean Hollister / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mN0HTI&quot;>;两个星期五前，我开车来到硅谷一栋矮矮的单层办公楼，去看一台 MacBook Air。我的演示室里没有保安，不需要证件，甚至连公关人员都没有。那是因为我去苹果总部并不是为了购买一台未发布的笔记本电脑。相反，我去了圣何塞参观了一台现有的 MacBook——一台经过手术改造的 MacBook，以证明一种奇异的冷却技术已经取得了多大的进步。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;qiPk2A&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;这款掌上电脑可能包含小工具冷却的未来&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/23/23733592/frore- airjet-zotac-mini-desktop-pc-zbox-pi430aj-price&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;GsUGuQ&quot;>;Frore Systems 是一家初创公司，年销售额达 1.16 亿美元资金，以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/23/23733592/frore-airjet-zotac-mini-desktop-pc-zbox-pi430aj-price&quot;>;我已经向您展示了它之前的首款产品&lt;/a>;：AirJet Mini 是一款压电冷却芯片，重量仅为 9 克，比两个美国 25 美分硬币叠在一起还要薄。每个标称消耗 1 瓦，可额外带走 4.25 瓦的热量。问题是：什么...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/27/23975368/frore-airjet-apple-macbook-air-fanless- mems&q